{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"61877af798","title":"中共复旦大学委员会关于孙大雨教授错划右派的改正结论","origin":"根据文件翻印件打印。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"107704cf8b","index":0,"year":1984,"month":7,"day":3,"articleId":"61877af798"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"27837de114","name":"(孙大雨)"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"301d83da45","type":"title","text":"中共复旦大学委员会关于孙大雨教授错划右派的改正结论","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"61877af798"},{"id":"c69cfc6f9f","type":"authors","text":"(孙大雨)","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"61877af798"},{"id":"67d2fda7ff","type":"paragraph","text":"孙大雨，男，一九○五年生，浙江诸暨人，一九四六年加入中国民主同盟，一九四七年参加上海大学教授联谊会，原为复旦大学外文系二级教授。一九五七年被划为右派分子，受降级降薪处分，现在华东师范大学任教。","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"61877af798"},{"id":"e83db2fbab","type":"paragraph","text":"根据中共中央一九七八年五十五号文件精神，经复查，孙大雨教授的右派问题属于错划，决定予以改正，恢复教授职称和高教二级的工资待遇。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"61877af798"},{"id":"33dd64df57","type":"paragraph","text":" 中共复旦大学委员会一九八四年七月三日","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"61877af798"}],"page":{"id":"0f50b459ad","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"61877af798","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}